```plantuml
@startuml XenitAB_git-auth-proxy
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "Git Client" as Client
rectangle "Kubernetes Cluster" as K8s {
  rectangle "Namespace" as NS {
    rectangle "Kubernetes Secret\n(Token)" as Secret
  }
  rectangle "Proxy Server" as Proxy
  rectangle "Prometheus Metrics" as Metrics
}

rectangle "Configuration" as Config
rectangle "Git Providers" as Providers {
  rectangle "GitHub" as GitHub
  rectangle "Azure DevOps" as AzureDevOps
}

Client -> Proxy: Clone/Push Request
Proxy -> Config: Load Configuration
Config --> Proxy: Org/Repo/Namespace Data
Proxy -> Secret: Validate Token
Secret --> Proxy: Token Valid/Invalid

Proxy -> Providers: Forward Request
Providers --> Proxy: Response
Proxy -> Client: Response

Proxy -> Metrics: Update Metrics
Metrics --> Prometheus: Expose Metrics

@enduml
```